  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\"><img alt=\"House Goodbrother.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/50px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/75px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/100px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Arthur Goodbrother</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\"><img alt=\"House Goodbrother.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/50px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/75px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/100px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\">House Goodbrother</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Arthur Goodbrother</b> was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\">House Goodbrother</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Arthur_Goodbrother&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/134_AC\" title=\"134 AC\">134&#160;AC</a> during Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Johanna_Lannister\" title=\"Johanna Lannister\">Johanna Lannister</a>'s invasion of the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a>, Arthur slew Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Leo_Costayne\" title=\"Leo Costayne\">Leo Costayne</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_admiral\" title=\"Lord admiral\">lord admiral</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>, on <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Wyk\" title=\"Great Wyk\">Great Wyk</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Arthur_Goodbrother&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7